title: Military history and oral histories combine for entertaining author presentation (Dubbo City Council)
text: ( Source : Dubbo City Council ) People with an interest in military history and recording and preserving the stories of people's memories should book early for the next Macquarie Regional Library author talk featuring Michael Caulfield.
